NAME
    RT-Extension-LocalDateHeader - [One line description of module's purpose
    here]

INSTALLATION
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install
        May need root permissions

    Edit your /opt/rt4/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm
        Add this line:

            Set(@Plugins, qw(RT::Extension::LocalDateHeader));

        or add "RT::Extension::LocalDateHeader" to your existing @Plugins
        line.

    patch RT
            patch /path/to/rt/share/html/Ticket/Element/ShowMessageHeaders < etc/callback_before_localization.diff

    Clear your mason cache
            rm -rf /opt/rt4/var/mason_data/obj

    Restart your webserver

